snippet.title: Amber Riley at TrevorLive! Red Carpet | What's Trending LIVE
snippet.description:
The Trevor Project's 15th Annual Trevor Live Gala- Amber Riley talks about her journey through bullying and Hollywood explaining that shaking hands and your given gifts will guide your future. Subscribe for more videos: http://full.sc/NfhdwD
